{"tid":4716,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖 她狂發淫蕩照求復合 男友受不了告上法院","createTime":"2016-11-26T15:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T20:21:04.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"601b09d27cac1b84a038810bf9c2b0db3091d174","tid":4716,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:17:31.000Z","msg":"英國一名30歲女子佩里(Nicole Peri)與25歲男友哈里斯(Timothy Harris)長年分分合合，佩里為求復合，對哈里斯狂發淫蕩照，並在1天之內奪命連環叩130通電話。哈里斯最後實在受不了，告上法院。<br />\n <br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，哈里斯和佩里正式分手後，佩里疑似氣不過，開始一系列「報復行動」。佩里對哈里斯寄出一連串淫蕩照和影片，希望哈里斯回心轉意，又要求見他一面。但哈里斯拒絕，並封鎖她的電話，佩里不甘心，就用其他電話號碼繼續轟炸哈里斯。哈里斯說，他總共收到300通連環CALL，更曾在一日之內收到130通來自佩裡的電話，「我實在逃不出佩里的魔爪」。<br />\n <br />\n哈里斯最後只好尋求司法途徑解決，佩里承認騷擾哈里斯，法官要她接受情緒管理課程，並頒佈1年禁制令，禁止她以任何方式聯絡哈里斯以及進入他家中。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160415/640_ba9425f95f3281626292509015fc7988.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160415%2F640_ba9425f95f3281626292509015fc7988.jpg&h=63522f47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://www.twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160415/640_9efafd9c59af8963700a9b7c2664386f.jpg[/img][img]www.twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160415/640_323957b103237f4ae5bc29c499f83ecc.jpg[/img][img]www.twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160415/640_46e169632a0abbca4352ef5947f3e729.jpg[/img][img]www.twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160415/640_549652eab23845277b3118bc444c912e.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160415%2F640_9efafd9c59af8963700a9b7c2664386f.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D%5Bimg%5Dwww.twimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160415%2F640_323957b103237f4ae5bc29c499f83ecc.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D%5Bimg%5Dwww.twimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160415%2F640_46e169632a0abbca4352ef5947f3e729.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D%5Bimg%5Dwww.twimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160415%2F640_549652eab23845277b3118bc444c912e.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=oC5AbjMi%2BH1TB